evant EQUATOR Network research reporting checklist(s) and other pertinent material as supplementary files, if applicable.YesCode to reproduce analyses will be posted on github (https://github.com/HopkinsIDD/serocovpop-households) and data will be made available upon request to the corresponding author. https://github.com/HopkinsIDD/serocovpop-households},
